      <div class="container">
        <h1>What Are We Doing?</h1>
				<br>
        <img src="https://www.insperity.com/wp-content/uploads/Mental_health1200x630.png" class="full" alt="">
				<div class="row" style="text-align:center;">
					<div class="container">
						<div class="col-md-4">
							<i style="font-size:35px" class="fas fa-users"></i>
							<br><b style="font-size:20px;"><%= v %><br>VOLUNTEERS</b><br>registered
						</div>

						<div class="col-md-4">
							<i style="font-size:35px" class="fas fa-smile-beam"></i>
							<br><b style="font-size:20px;">11<br>ACTIVITIES</b><br>made available
						</div>
						<div class="col-md-4">
							<i style="font-size:35px" class="fas fa-blog"></i>
							<br><b style="font-size:20px;"><%= b %><br>BLOGS</b><br>written
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<br>

				<div class="row">
					<div class="col-sm-6">
						HelpingHand's motive is to help people through-out the world by providing a platform to fight and overcome the stigma related to mental-health. The motive of this website is to help the people suffering from mental-illness in any possible way we can. HelpingHands have tied hands with several organisations to promote mind-relaxing acrivities. Also people can volunteer themselves to help the sufferers, or spread awarness through blogs.
						<br><b>Volunteering - </b>HelpingHands believe that together we can bring a change in society. Hence we provide you a platform to get involved with the initiative taken by HelpingHands for mental health in a number of ways, depending on your area of interest and your capacity. To volunteer, partner with us or support us, please fill the form given in the Volnteering section.
					</div>
					<div class="col-sm-6">
						<b>Activities - </b>Mental health activities are things you can do to improve your mental health. Engaging in wellness activities can have a positive effect on your health and wellness, as well as your sense of inner peace. HelpingHands has tied hands with several organisation where you can perform these activities. You just need to fill out a form for registering yourself in these activities.
						<br><b>Blogs - </b>For the large Indian population to be involved in its own mental health, the only way forward is through enhancing mental health awareness. With rising awareness, it can be expected that early recognition and access to treatment will follow, as will the adoption of preventive measures. Therefore, we have opened a portal for you to write your point of views and spread the right messages through out the world.
					</div>
				</div>

