      <div class="container">
      <h1>How You Can Contribute?</h1>
      <img src="https://sabrangindia.in/sites/default/files/field/image/mentalhealth-crop-1200x649.jpg" class="full">
			Every small effort makes a difference across the world! Your small effort can help the suffers to win the battle against mental illness and help the world to become a better place. Here are some things one can do to contribute in this battle:-
				<ul class="fa-ul" style="list-style:none;">
				<li><span class="fa-li"><i class="fas fa-arrow-circle-right"></i></span><b>Talk Out! - </b>The most important thing one can do is to talk to the sufferer and help them overcome the situation.</li>
				<li><span class="fa-li"><i class="fas fa-arrow-circle-right"></i></span><b>Report fraud - </b>Report fraudulent Covid-19 tests, vaccines and treatments and become a responsible citizen of the country!</li>
				<li><span class="fa-li"><i class="fas fa-arrow-circle-right"></i></span><b>Donate - </b>There are severa organisations out there that need monetary help to fight this battle. Donate there </li>
				<li><span class="fa-li"><i class="fas fa-arrow-circle-right"></i></span><b>Voluteer - </b>If you are willing to help the people out here then be a volunteer in this battle. </li>
					<li><span class="fa-li"><i class="fas fa-arrow-circle-right"></i></span><b>Be Polite - </b>People with depression are already suffering. The least you can do is be polite with them.</li>
				<li><span class="fa-li"><i class="fas fa-arrow-circle-right"></i></span><b>Spread Awareeness - </b>Spread right informaion about mental health issues among people as there is so many misleading/wrong info flooding across people.</li>
			</ul>
